des:
Kick-Box-Move Fitness has a variety of audio workouts that will have you fit and fighting for life. These workouts include kicking, boxing, moving and more. Our program has some great health benefits that include: burn calories and lose weight, improve cardio, lower blood pressure, increase strength, improve mobility, and improve flexibility.

To get started, just ask Alexa:
- Alexa, open kick box move
- Alexa, launch kick box move

For more Free and On Demand workout videos visit our website at www.kickboxmove.com
